{Grimlock}
Cargo Hold

    A large mound of crates and debris shifted to one side as something
large beneath it began exerting a great amount of force to shift itself from
the rubble, the gravelly voice was part command and part threat as it spoke,
"Me Grimlock say stop shouting, me say audio receptors still hurting!"

    The rubble shifted and was thrown back as the being identified as
Grimlock shook himself free of the debris, the robotic t-rex shaking the
last bits from it's body before turning to look at Daytripper, "Me Grimlock
no like stupid pilot....movie no good either."
